{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "4.920", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Danke, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "4.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.000", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.560", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.680", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "K\u00fcrzlich berichtete mir ein junger Mann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.120", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass er zu seiner Ausbildungsstelle t\u00e4glich schwarzfahren m\u00fcsse, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.360", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sein Lehrlingsgehalt reiche nicht f\u00fcr den Kauf eines Monatstickets. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.240", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nun f\u00fcrchtet er, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.360", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wegen mehrfachen Schwarzfahrens in den Knast zu kommen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.320", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn nach \u00a7\u00a0265a des Strafgesetzbuches droht demjenigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.880", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der ohne Ticket f\u00e4hrt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.080", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ein Jahr Freiheitsstrafe oder eine Geldstrafe. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.080", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Folge f\u00fcr den jungen Mann w\u00e4re der Verlust seiner Ausbildungsstelle und damit die Arbeitslosigkeit. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.560", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieser Auszubildende f\u00e4hrt nicht schwarz, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.720", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil er irgendeine kriminelle Energie hat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.960", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er f\u00e4hrt ohne Ticket, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.960", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil er kein Geld daf\u00fcr hat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.480", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So was geh\u00f6rt nicht bestraft. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.520", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Schwarzfahren geh\u00f6rt raus aus dem Strafgesetzbuch."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.160", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dazu haben wir heute einen Gesetzentwurf vorgelegt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.440", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich m\u00f6chte ihnen drei weitere Gr\u00fcnde nennen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.240", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die f\u00fcr unseren Gesetzentwurf sprechen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.400", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Erstens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.040", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer schwarzparkt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.640", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "also falsch parkt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.120", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der zahlt ein Bu\u00dfgeld zwischen 10 und 25\u00a0Euro. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.840", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit ist die Sache erledigt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.840", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Falschparken ist eine Ordnungswidrigkeit. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.040", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Schwarzfahren hingegen ist eine Straftat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.680", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer es macht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.600", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "muss also nicht nur die Vertragsstrafe\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.320", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das erh\u00f6hte Bef\u00f6rderungsentgelt\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.640", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "von etwa 60\u00a0Euro bezahlen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.920", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ihm droht zus\u00e4tzlich ein Strafverfahren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.760", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das wirkt auf den Betroffenen wie eine Doppelbestrafung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "100.800", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei haben Schwarzfahren und Schwarzparken in etwa den gleichen Unrechtsgehalt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "100.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.960", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei beidem gibt es keine besondere kriminelle Energie. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.360", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es darf nicht sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.200", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Schwarzfahren deutlich h\u00e4rter bestraft wird als Falschparken. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.280", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist ungerecht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "115.520", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zweitens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "115.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.200", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Verkehrsunternehmen haben zivilrechtliche M\u00f6glichkeiten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "119.720", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ihr Geld einzutreiben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "119.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "122.000", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie k\u00f6nnen Schwarzfahrer auf Zahlung verklagen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "122.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.120", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zudem erheben sie die besagten 60\u00a0Euro Vertragsstrafe. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.480", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Verkehrsunternehmen haben also rechtliche M\u00f6glichkeiten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "131.880", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ihre Anspr\u00fcche durchzusetzen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "131.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.520", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihnen geht es nicht anders als anderen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.880", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denen gegen\u00fcber ein Vertrag gebrochen wird; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "140.200", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch sie sind selbst zust\u00e4ndig f\u00fcrs Geldeintreiben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "140.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.360", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Strafrecht benutzen die Verkehrsunternehmen als M\u00f6glichkeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.120", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kosten zu sparen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.520", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Denn die Ermittlungen durch Polizei und Justiz gegen den jeweiligen Schwarzfahrer zahlt der Steuerzahler. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.520", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit muss endlich Schluss sein."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.320", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Drittens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.120", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das \u00dcbelste an diesem Straftatbestand ist: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.960", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er richtet sich gegen arme Menschen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.960", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer nur eine kleine Rente hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.120", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wer nur ein kleines Azubigehalt bezieht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.600", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der kann sich oft kein Ticket leisten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.160", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Beim kargen Hartz-IV-Satz sind gerade einmal 26\u00a0Euro f\u00fcr Mobilit\u00e4t vorgesehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.640", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wo k\u00f6nnen Sie denn daf\u00fcr ein Monatsticket kaufen? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.040", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Menschen m\u00fcssen aber mobil sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.320", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil sie zum Amt m\u00fcssen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.680", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil sie zu Bewerbungsgespr\u00e4chen m\u00fcssen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.960", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Laut einer Studie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.880", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in Auftrag gegeben von der Landesregierung NRW, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "190.320", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sind 58\u00a0Prozent der Menschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "190.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.440", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die wegen Schwarzfahrens verurteilt werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "193.480", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hartz-IV-Empf\u00e4nger, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "193.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.760", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "21\u00a0Prozent sind obdachlos. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.000", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist unertr\u00e4glich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.600", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Menschen wegen ihres leeren Geldbeutels bestraft werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.280", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Armut darf keine Straftat sein."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.120", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00dcbrigens: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.200", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nat\u00fcrlich verurteilen die Gerichte die Betroffenen meist zu einer Geldstrafe und nicht zu einer Gef\u00e4ngnisstrafe. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.080", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber wer sich kein Ticket leisten kann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.200", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der kann auch nicht die Geldstrafe zahlen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.640", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer aber die verh\u00e4ngte Geldstrafe nicht bezahlt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "224.160", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dem droht die Ersatzfreiheitsstrafe; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "224.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.200", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der muss also das Ganze im Knast absitzen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.360", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bundesweit sitzen nach Angaben der NRW-Landesregierung 5\u00a0000\u00a0Menschen wegen Bef\u00f6rderungserschleichung im Gef\u00e4ngnis. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.640", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jeder Tag Haft kostet pro Gefangenen 130\u00a0Euro. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.800", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bundesweit werden j\u00e4hrlich 200\u00a0Millionen Euro daf\u00fcr ausgegeben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "247.560", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Menschen in den Knast zu stecken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "247.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.640", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die ihre Geldstrafe nicht zahlen konnten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.080", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist doch irrsinnig!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "253.440", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kollege, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "253.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.200", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kommen Sie zum Schluss, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.320", 
   "id": "s000089", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bitte."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "255.360", 
   "id": "s000090", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
